<br>
You want to play a High Elf.  Guess what, in Everquest, the high elves are good, they are noble, if a bit arrogant, and upright.  The Dark Elves are evil and nasty, the Trolls are monsterous and eat people, the Iksar hate everyone and the hate is returned, etc.  You are playing Everquest, think of it being kind of like chess.  You might WANT your Knight to move like a Queen, but it doesn't, and paying 10 bucks a month doesn't change those rules no matter how you wish. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ukelson13.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelson13</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/2/01 6:29:24 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: FV Server Complaint...</span><hr size=1> &quot;i am sorry you &quot;hate&quot; this view i have, yet i am not asking you to like it. i just wanted to rp something a little more open minded than yourself. rest assured that the FV server will maintain this integrity you so crave. nothing but squeaky clean high elves everywhere....&quot;<br>
